FILE PATH[odoo/fields.py]

1 index
name = fields.Char(string="Name", index=True)
name: This field has index=True, meaning an index will be created on this column in the database. Searching by name will be faster.

precompute parameter







Relational Fields
---------------------------
Many2one
--------
- use in child model and it set foreign keys
- default store in db.

One2many is not store in db.
Many2many is not store in db.

ondelete 
--------
(no action,set default)

Many2one 
- restrict
- cascade
- set null

Many2many
- restrict
- cascade (not sence)

One2many
- restrict

domain
-------
domain="[('parent_model_field','CONDITION',current_model_field)]"
ex 1: domain="[('active_status', '=', True)]"
ex 2: private_state_id = fields.Many2one("res.country.state",domain="[('country_id', '=?', private_country_id)]")
      private_country_id = fields.Many2one("res.country", string="Private Country", groups="hr.group_hr_user")



widget = many2many_binary
--------------------------
binary_multi_file = fields.Many2many(comodel_name='ir.attachment')
<field name="binary_multi_file" widget="many2many_binary"/>


